'- Board President, DBSV Red Socks (Aug 2020-Jul 2021). Club operations during COVID-19.\n\n' +
'QUALIFICATIONS:\n' +
'- DFB: C-Lizenz Profil Jugend (completing March 2026), Basis-Coach, Kindertrainerzertifikat, Torwarttrainerzertifikat, Basis-Vereinsmanager\n' +
