var CL_TEMPLATES = {
  'Football Coaching': 'Para 1: Express interest in [org] as [role]. Sport science + coaching/youth dev across Europe. Club mission. Para 2: Maastricht (physiology, injury, data analysis, UCLan Cyprus thesis on injury detection). MSc Football Science Southampton Solent (physiology, biomechanics, talent ID, team leadership, rehab). Dissertation PRISMA 2020 bio-banding systematic review, submitted Aug 2025, PhD proposal with Dr Nuno Nunes. Para 3 (PERSONALISE): 1-2 specific experiences. Options: SG Unterrath/KFC Uerdingen for academy; AFC Stoneham for senior women; Itchen College for education-linked; Fussball Futures for grassroots. Mention DFB C-Lizenz (completing Mar 2026) for German clubs. Para 4: Coached U11s to senior women across cultures/languages, third language. Scientific grounding, DFB licences, evidence-based youth dev.',
  'Athletic Training / S&C': 'Para 1: Interest in [org] as [role]. Sport science + athletic dev/performance monitoring across Europe. Germany, Netherlands, UK cross-cultural adaptability. Para 2: Maastricht physiology, injury, quantitative data analysis, MATLAB (glucose dynamics, genome-scale metabolic modelling COBRA Toolbox, R). UCLan Cyprus thesis on injury detection using isometric strength testing. MSc Football Science: physiology, biomechanics, S&C, rehab, training demands, GPS/LPS Catapult. Partial BASES accreditation. Para 3 (PERSONALISE): On-pitch/gym athletic dev, load management, data-driven programming. Options: Catapult/GPS from MSc; warm-up/athletic dev at AFC Stoneham and SG Unterrath; conditioning at Itchen College and KFC Uerdingen. Para 4: Pedagogical dimension of athletic training - practitioners are educators. Cross-cultural coaching, diverse relationships.',
  'Education / Teaching': 'Para 1: Apply for [role] at [school]. TA at ISD - school where completed own secondary education. Drawn to [school] because [IB curriculum/multilingual/inclusive]. Para 2: Current TA at ISD - classroom support elementary level, different learning needs, independent lesson coverage. CPD when available. Consistency, clear communication, sensitivity. Para 3: Coaching 6-17 years across England, Germany, Netherlands. Structured progressive programmes, differentiating for developmental stages, pastoral support. Itchen College Girls (formal college); Fussball Futures (safeguarding, parent communication). Para 4: Fluent English/Spanish, proficient German, conversational Dutch. Committed to professional dev in education.',
  'Youth Work / Social Dev': 'Para 1: Interest in [role] at [org]. Several years with young people in sport, education, community settings in Germany, Netherlands, England. Drawn to [org] because [community-first/social dev/underserved youth]. Para 2: Fussball Futures - multi-day camps children 6-12 since 2021. Programme design, safeguarding, logistics, parent comms, supervising junior staff. TA at ISD - structured classroom support, different learning needs. Para 3: Coaching U11-U17 Germany and senior women England - relationships outside the activity. Supporting players through setbacks, diverse squad dynamics. MSc dissertation bio-banding - psychological and sociological outcomes critically under-studied. FA Safeguarding, Emergency First Aid. Para 4: Fluent English/Spanish, proficient German, conversational Dutch. Four countries.',
  'Data Analysis / Research': 'Para 1: Apply for [role] at [org]. Quantitative scientific training + applied performance analysis + hands-on coaching - unusual technical and practical combination. Para 2: Maastricht quantitative methods: MATLAB R2021a - 1M parameter combinations E-DES ODE model insulin-regulated glucose dynamics, PID controller, parallelised computation. MATLAB COBRA Toolbox: genome-scale metabolic models arrhythmogenic cardiomyopathy from RNA-seq, GIMME/iMAT/E-Flux, gene ontology DAVID/REVIGO/PathVisio, preprocessing in R. MSc: GPS/LPS Catapult. Para 3 (PERSONALISE): GPS load data KFC Uerdingen; Veo video analysis scouting; performance tracking. MSc dissertation PRISMA 2020 bio-banding, 1122 papers 5 databases, submitted Aug 2025. PhD proposal Dr Nuno Nunes. Para 4: Communicate findings to practitioners - background as coach means knowing questions coaches need answered. Partial BASES accreditation reapplying.',
  'Other': 'Write a professional tailored cover letter based on the applicant background in sport science, coaching, and research. Match relevant experience to role requirements.'
